Dịka ntuliaka ọkwa onyeisiala na ndị ụlọomeiwu Naịjirịa na-aga n'ihu taa bụ 25 Febụwarị 2023, ndị mmadụ ga na-atụ anya ihe ga-abụ mpụtara ntuliaka ndị a.
BBC Igbo ga na-egosi mpụtara ntuliaka ndị a dịka ụlọọrụ na-ahazi ntuliaka bụ Independent National Electoral Commission (Inec) ga na-akpọpụta ha.
Pịa aka n'aka maka mpụtara ntuliaka ọkwa ndị ụlọomeiwu

Ndị Naịjirịa ga-atụ vootu na ntuliaka n'ụbọchị Satọde. Mmadụ iri na asatọ na-azọ ọkwa Onyeisiala ebe ọtụtụ ndị ọzọ na-azọ ọkwa sịnetị na nke ụlọomeiwu nta. BBC ji ọnụọgụgụ si n'aka ụlọọrụ Independent National Electoral Commission (Inec) egosipụta mpụtara ndị a.
Iji merie n'agba mbụ, onye na-azọ ọkwa aghaghị inwete vootu kachasị n'ọnụọgụgụ nakwa vootu karịrị 25% n'ime ọkara abụọ ma e kee steetị 36 gụnyere isiobodo Abuja ụzọ atọ
